      "title": "ElizaOS Discord Community Activity - June 24, 2026",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "A user named Fixer posted an identical recruitment message in both the general discussion and coders channels, seeking an English-speaking client liaison for a development team expanding into the U.S. market. The role required no coding skills, only communication and organizational abilities, with flexible hours and performance-based compensation. The post was met with skepticism, including a sarcastic reply questioning the poster's English proficiency, and community moderators flagged the user along with another account as potential scammers, tagging a moderator for action.",
