          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "In the general discussion channel, community members raised ongoing concerns about the elizaOS token, with one user asking about staking and token utility features, expressing frustration over the long wait. Another user simply asked if the token was still alive. A community member responded positively, stating the project was in good health. A separate user in the coders channel requested a direct message from a team member without further elaboration.",
